<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Welcome to Demo Server</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      color: #111;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    header {
      background-color: #d22128;
      padding: 20px;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
    }

    header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 2.5em;
    }

    nav {
      background-color: #333;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 10px 0;
    }

    nav a {
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin: 0 15px;
      font-size: 1em;
    }

    nav a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    main {
      max-width: 960px;
      margin: 30px auto;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }

    main h2 {
      color: #d22128;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }

    footer {
      background-color: #f3f3f3;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 0.9em;
      color: #555;
      border-top: 1px solid #ccc;
    }

    ul.links {
      list-style-type: none;
      padding: 0;
    }

    ul.links li {
      margin: 5px 0;
    }

    ul.links li a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #005eb8;
    }

    ul.links li a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <h1>Welcome to the Demo Application Server</h1>
  <p>Powered by NGINX • Secured with SSL • Backed by Express</p>
  <div>
    <h2>IP Address: <%= ip %></h2>
    <p>Hostname: <%= hostname %></p>
  </div>
</header>

<nav>
  <a href="#">Home</a>
  <a href="#">Documentation</a>
  <a href="#">Downloads</a>
  <a href="#">API Reference</a>
  <a href="#">Support</a>
</nav>

<main>
  <h2>About This Server</h2>
  <p>This is a demonstration landing page for a containerized web service using NGINX as a reverse proxy and Express.js as the backend server. It supports HTTPS traffic and dynamic service registration.</p>

  <h2>Documentation</h2>
  <ul class="links">
    <li><a href="#">Getting Started Guide</a></li>
    <li><a href="#">REST API Docs</a></li>
    <li><a href="#">Deployment Instructions</a></li>
    <li><a href="#">Service Health Monitoring</a></li>
    <li><a href="#">Security and Certificates</a></li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Useful Links</h2>
  <ul class="links">
    <li><a href="#">Project GitHub Repo</a></li>
    <li><a href="#">Nginx Configuration Templates</a></li>
    <li><a href="#">Consul Service Registry</a></li>
    <li><a href="#">Load Testing with Apache Bench</a></li>
  </ul>

  
</main>

<footer>
  <p>&copy; 2025 DemoApp Technologies. All rights reserved.</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
